data.title: BAD BAD BAD!!!
data.text:
This place was our first stop when we arrived in Los Angeles, I don't understand this place has such a big menu but when we were there they only had three items available beef chicken and pork, I ordered the al pastor tacos and let me tell you they were terrible terrible barely any words to describe how bad they were the preparation of the meat was just terrible the fresh pan dulce they sell no flavor at all overall very bad experience, 

Going there no mad!!!!!!

data.title: Aguas frescas, cafe de olla, pan dulce 😋
data.text: Cada ves que visito el area de Los angeles debo visitar El gallo giro en Lynwood!! Me encanta la variedad de aguas frescas! El cafe de olla, su pan dulce!! Sus tortas! Solo de recordarme quisiera ir pero vivo casi a 3,000 millas de distancia!! No puedo dejar de mencional el buen trato de las personas trabajando! Amables y con una sonrisa! Tambien hacen unas sopas muy buenas!!! Asi que en lo personal lo recomiendo al 100%
